<p>Our people are awesome, yours are awesome. Let’s agree that both parties agree to withhold from recruiting employees from each other’s organizations throughout the working relationship and one year following completion of the contractual agreement. &nbsp;The fee for violating this portion of the agreement is 20% of the employee’s first year salary and reasonably expected commissions to be paid in full, due on the date of hire and will stand regardless of how long they work for the new organization.</p>
<br><h2 class="da-service__title ">Transfers</h>
<p>You cannot transfer this contract to anyone else without our permission. This contract stays in place and need not be renewed. If for some reason one part of this contract becomes invalid or unenforceable, the remaining parts of it remain in place.</p>
